oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: W. T. C. B. I. Country Jamboree at Ft. Homer W Hesterly Armory
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Metal photoplates; Sovine, Red; Wells, Kitty; Dudley, Dave;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing the WTCBI Country Jamboree with Red Sovine, Bonnie Lee, Dave Dudley, Kitty Wells, and Johnny and Bobby Wright at the Fort Homer West Hesterly Armory on November 24, 25, 26, and 27. Poster features metal photoplates of Red Sovine, Dave Duddley, Kitty Wells, and Johnny Wright.
